        <!--
          Koma's own update feed. The previous contents mirrored upstream Palmier releases
          (palmier-io) signed with upstream's key — removed so the updater never offers the
          upstream app in place of Koma.

          scripts/release.sh appends a signed <item> here per Koma release. Before publishing the
          first one: generate Koma's Sparkle key, set SUPublicEDKey in Info.plist to the matching
          public key, and sign the DMG with the private key (kept out of the repo). Releases must
          be code-signed with the Koma/Kibo Developer ID and uploaded to this repo's GitHub
          releases — not buildable from the sandboxed dev shell (ad-hoc signing only).
        -->
    </channel>
